(239, '001-006', 'BREWERS YEAST', 'حبوب الخميرة', '<div class=\"row item-row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>10 Grain, 650 mg</li>\r\n<li>Nutritional Supplement</li>\r\n<li>Easier to Swallow Tablet</li>\r\n<li>Non-GMO</li>\r\n<li>A Dietary Supplement</li>\r\n<li>Vegetarian - Vegan</li>\r\n<li>Kosher</li>\r\n<li>General Health</li>\r\n<li>Family Owned Since 1968</li>\r\n<li>GMP Quality Assured</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>NOW&reg; Brewer\'s Yeast has several naturally occurring vitamins and minerals, with most notably B-vitamins. In addition, Brewer\'s Yeast offers other components, such as amino acids and beta-glucans. No synthetic vitamins are added to the yeast during processing. NOW&reg; Brewer\'s Yeast is a Genuine Whole Food Supplement.</p>\r\n<p>Brewer\'s Yeast has naturally occurring B-vitamins such as: Thiamin (Vitamin B-1), Riboflavin (Vitamin B-2), Niacin, Vitamin B-6, Folic Acid, Biotin and Pantothenic Acid.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row item-row\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3><strong>Suggested Use</strong></h3>\r\n<div class=\"prodOverviewDetail\">\r\n<p>Take 3 tablets 3 times daily with food.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row item-row\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3><strong>Other Ingredients</strong></h3>\r\n<div class=\"prodOverviewIngred\">\r\n<p>Hydroxypropyl cellulose, stearic acid (vegetable source), croscarmellose sodium, magnesium stearate (vegetable source) and silicon dioxide.</p>\r\nContains wheat. Brewer\'s yeast is derived from barley and wheat.<br /><br />Not manufactured with soy, milk, egg, fish, shellfish or tree nut ingredients. Produced in a GMP facility that processes other ingredients containing these allergens.<br /><br /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row item-row\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3><strong>Warnings</strong></h3>\r\n<div class=\"prodOverviewDetail\">\r\n<p><strong>Caution:</strong>&nbsp;For adults only. Brewer\'s Yeast has significant amounts of tyramine. Consult physician if taking an MAO inhibitor or other medication, if pregnant/nursing, or if you have Crohn\'s Disease, or other medical condition. Keep out of reach of children.</p>\r\n<p>Natural color variation may occur in this product.</p>\r\n<p>Store in a cool, dry place after opening.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row item-row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Disclaimer</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"disclaimer\" class=\"prodOverviewDetail\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">While iHerb strives to ensure the accuracy of its product images and information, some manufacturing changes to packaging and/or ingredients may be pending update on our site. Although items may occasionally ship with alternate packaging, freshness is always guaranteed. We recommend that you read labels, warnings and directions of all products before use and not rely solely on the information provided by iHerb.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '<div class=\"row item-row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3><strong>الوصف</strong></h3>\r\n<div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>10 حبوب، 650 ملجم</li>\r\n<li>مكمل غذائي</li>\r\n<li>أقراص سهلة البلع</li>\r\n<li>غير معدل وراثيًا</li>\r\n<li>مكمل غذائي</li>\r\n<li>نباتي - مناسب للنباتيين</li>\r\n<li>كوشر</li>\r\n<li>الصحة العامة</li>\r\n<li>شركة تملكها الأسرة منذ عام 1968</li>\r\n<li>جودة مضمونة وفقًا لممارسات التصنيع الجيدة</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>تحتوي خميرة البيرة من NOW&reg; على العديد من الفيتامينات والمعادن التي تنتج بشكل طبيعي، وأبرزها فيتامينات ب. بالإضافة إلى ذلك، تقدم خميرة البيرة مكونات أخرى، مثل الأحماض الأمينية وبيتا جلوكانات. لا يتم إضافة فيتامينات اصطناعية إلى الخميرة أثناء المعالجة. خميرة البيرة من NOW&reg; هي مكمل غذائي أصلي كامل.</p>\r\n<p>تحتوي خميرة البيرة على فيتامينات ب التي تنت