(358, '001-125', 'APPLE CIDER VINEGAR JARROW 473 ML', 'APPLE CIDER VINEGAR JARROW 473 ML', '<div class=\"row item-row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Unpasteurized &amp; Unfiltered with \"Vinegar Mother\"</li>\r\n<li>Vegan</li>\r\n<li>USDA Organic</li>\r\n<li>Gluten Free</li>\r\n<li>Certified Organic by QAI</li>\r\n<li>Suitable for Vegetarians/Vegans</li>\r\n<li>5% Acidity Full Strength Apple Cider Vinegar</li>\r\n<li>Zero Calories per Serving</li>\r\n<li>No Chemicals, Additives, Preservatives</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Jarrow Formulas Organic Apple Cider Vinegar with \"Vinegar Mother\" is produced without any chemicals, additives or preservatives. Jarrow Formulas Organic Apple Cider Vinegar is made using yeast and bacteria to ferment apple juice. The microorganisms produce acetic acid, and the final product is apple cider vinegar. \"Vinegar Mother\" consists of strands of proteins, enzymes and microbes from the fermentation process. Unpasteurized and unfiltered, Jarrow Formulas\' Organic Apple Cider Vinegar maintains its natural properties.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row item-row\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3><strong>Suggested Use</strong></h3>\r\n<div class=\"prodOverviewDetail\">\r\n<p>Shake well before using to distribute the \"Vinegar Mother\". Use in salad dressings, marinades, sauces, beverages or pickling. Natural vinegar comes in many shades: color variation is normal.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row item-row\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3><strong>Other Ingredients</strong></h3>\r\n<div class=\"prodOverviewIngred\">\r\n<p>Organic unfiltered apple cider vinegar.</p>\r\n<p>No wheat, gluten, no dairy, no soybeans, no egg, no fish/shellfish, no peanuts/tree nuts.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row item-row\">\r\n<d