(386, '002-018', 'E OIL 70000', 'زيت فيتامين E 70000', '<div class=\"row item-row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>31,500 mg | 70,000 IU</li>\r\n<li>Moisturizes Dry Skin</li>\r\n<li>For Topical Use</li>\r\n<li>Product Not Tested on Animals</li>\r\n<li>Vegetarian</li>\r\n<li>Non-GMO</li>\r\n<li>No Gluten</li>\r\n<li>No Artificial Color</li>\r\n<li>No Preservatives</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Clean Nutrition</strong><br /><br />Sundown&reg; believes in clean nutrition and being transparent. That\'s why you won\'t find genetically modified ingredients, gluten, wheat, dairy, lactose or artificial flavors in any of our products.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row item-row\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3><strong>Suggested Use</strong></h3>\r\n<div class=\"prodOverviewDetail\">\r\n<p>Apply generously and gently massage into skin for maximum penetration.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row item-row\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3><strong>Other Ingredients</strong></h3>\r\n<div class=\"prodOverviewIngred\">\r\n<p>Tocopheryl acetate (vitamin E).</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row item-row\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3><strong>Warnings</strong></h3>\r\n<div class=\"prodOverviewDetail\">\r\n<p>Do not apply to broken, or irritated skin or areas affected by rashes. Discontinue use and consult your doctor if skin sensitivity occurs. Avoid contact with eyes. Do not use on children or animals.</p>\r\n<p>For external use only. Do not ingest. Keep out of reach of children.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row item-row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Disclaimer</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"disclaimer\" class=\"prodOverviewDetail\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left