(452, '002-070', 'Now green  tea tree oil', 'زيت الشاي الاخضر ناو', '<div class=\"row item-row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>100% Australian</li>\r\n<li>Melaleuca Alternifolia</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Our Tea Tree Oil is prepared from the fresh (undried) leaf of Melaleuca alternifolia trees which are Traditionally Grown in their natural habitat in Australia.</p>\r\n<p>The leaf is hand-harvested at its optimal potency and is then promptly steam-distilled to produce the finest oil possible - solvents are never used.</p>\r\n<p>Our Tea Tree Oil is low in cineole (less than 7%) and is therefore very gentle to the skin and mucous membranes.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row item-row\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3><strong>Suggested Use</strong></h3>\r\n<div class=\"prodOverviewDetail\">\r\n<p>Shake well before using</p>\r\n<p>Use sparingly - a little goes a long way.</p>\r\n<p>Apply full strength or, for sensitive areas, dilute with vegetable oil.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row item-row\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3><strong>Other Ingredients</strong></h3>\r\n<div class=\"prodOverviewIngred\">\r\n<p>Tea Tree essential oil.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row item-row\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3><strong>Warnings</strong></h3>\r\n<div class=\"prodOverviewDetail\">\r\n<p>For external use only.</p>\r\n<p>May stain clothing.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Caution:</strong>&nbsp;Keep away from eyes and mucous membranes.</p>\r\n<p>Keep out of the reach of children</p>\r\n<p>Store away from heat &amp; light</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row item-row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Disclaimer</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"disclaimer\" class=\"prodOver