(479, '002-094', 'Lemon oil and eucalyptus 30 ml', 'زيت الليمون والكافور 30 مل', '<div class=\"row item-row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Essential Oils</li>\r\n<li>Eucalyptus Citriodora</li>\r\n<li>Purity Tested-Quality Assured</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Aroma:&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;Citronella-like with subtle floral undertones.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Attributes:&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;Refreshing, cleansing, stimulating.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Mixes well With:&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;Geranium, lavender, cedarwood, rosemary, mint and tree oils.</p>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;Extraction Method:&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;Steam distilled from leaves and twigs.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row item-row\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3><strong>Suggested Use</strong></h3>\r\n<div class=\"prodOverviewDetail\">\r\n<p>For aromatherapy use. For all other uses, carefully dilute with a carrier oil such as jojoba, grapeseed, or almond oil prior to use. Please consult an essential oil book or other professional reference source for suggested dilution ratios.</p>\r\n<p>Natural essential oils are highly concentrated and should be used with care.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row item-row\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3><strong>Warnings</strong></h3>\r\n<div class=\"prodOverviewDetail\">\r\n<p><strong>Caution:&nbsp;</strong>Keep out of reach of children. Do not apply on children\'s skin, especially the face, mouth, nose and eyes. Avoid contact with eyes. If pregnant or nursing, consult your healthcare practitioner before using.</p>\r\n<p>Not for internal use.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row item-row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Disclaimer</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"disclaimer\" class=\"prodOverviewDetail\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">While iHerb strives to ensure the accuracy of its product images and information, some manufacturing changes to packaging and/or ingredients may be pending update on our site. Although items may occasionally ship with alternate packaging, freshness is always guaranteed. We recommend that you read labels, warnings and directions of all products before use and not rely solely on the information provided by iHerb.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '<div class=\"row item-row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3><strong>الوصف</strong></h3>\r\n<div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Essential Oils</li>\r\n<li>Eucalyptus Citriodora</li>\r\n<li>Purity Tested-Quality Assured</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Aroma:&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;Citronella-like with subtle floral undertones.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Attributes:&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;Refreshing, cleansing, stimulating.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Mixes well With:&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;Geranium, lavender, cedarwood, rosemary, mint and tree oils.</p>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;Extraction Method:&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;Steam distilled from leaves and twigs.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row item-row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3><strong>طريقة الاستخدام</strong></h3>\r\n<div class=\"prodOverviewDetail\">\r\n<p>للاستعمال في العلاج بالعطور. لكل الاستخدامات الأخرى، قم بعناية بحل الزيت بزيت حامل مثل الجوجوبا، بذور العنب، أو اللوز قبل الاستخدام. الرجاء مراجعة أحد كتب الزيوت العطرية أو أحد المصادر المرجعية المتخصصة الأخرى للتعرف على نسب المزج المقترحة.</p>\r\n<p>الزيوت العطرية الطبيعية شديدة التركيز ويجب استخدامها بحرص.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row item-row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3><strong>تحذيرات</strong></h3>\r\n<div class=\"prodOverviewDetail\">\r\n<p><strong>تحذير:</strong>&nbsp;يُحفظ بعيداً عن متناول الأطفال. لا تضعه على بشرة الأطفال، خاصة الوجه، القم والأنف والعينين. تجنب ملامسة العينين. يوصى باستشارة ممارس الرعاية الصحية قبل الاستعمال؛ في حالة الحمل أو الإرضاع.</p>\r\n<p>غير مخصص للا