(1202, '009-288', 'Carmex Daily Care Moisturizing Lip Balm 3*1', 'مرطب شفايف بنكهات متنوعه 3*1 CARMEX', '<div class=\"row item-row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>SPF 15 Sunscreen</li>\r\n<li>Water Resistant (80 Minutes)</li>\r\n<li>Fresh Cherry - Strawberry - Wintergreen</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Uses:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Helps protect against sunburn.</li>\r\n<li>High SPF gives more sunburn protection.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row item-row\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3><strong>Suggested Use</strong></h3>\r\n<div class=\"prodOverviewDetail\">\r\n<p>Apply liberally 15 minutes before sun exposure.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Reapply:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>After 80 minutes of swimming or sweating.</li>\r\n<li>Immediately after towel drying.</li>\r\n<li>At least every 2 hours.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Children under 2 years of age: ask a doctor.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row item-row\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3><strong>Other Ingredients</strong></h3>\r\n<div class=\"prodOverviewIngred\">\r\n<table border=\"1\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<td width=\"50%\"><strong>Active Ingredients</strong></td>\r\n<td width=\"50%\"><strong>Purpose</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<td>Octinoxate 7.50%</td>\r\n<td>Sunscreen</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<td>Oxybenzone 4.00%</td>\r\n<td>Sunscreen</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<td colspan=\"2\"><strong>Inactive Ingredients</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<td colspan=\"2\"><strong>Fresh Cherry, Strawberry:&nbsp;</strong>Petrolatum, lanolin, euphorbia cerifera wax, isopropyl palmitate, ozokerite, flavor