(1225, '009-059-007', 'ST IVES  Green Tea & Bamboo Scrub Blackhead Clearing', 'ST IVES مقشر البامبو & الشاي الأخضر للتخلص من الرؤوس السوداء', '<div class=\"row item-row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Enhanced with Bamboo &amp; Walnut Shell Exfoliants</li>\r\n<li>Made with 100% Natural Exfoliants</li>\r\n<li>Oil-Free Salicylic Acid Acne Medication</li>\r\n<li>Clears Blackheads &amp; Unclogs Pores</li>\r\n<li>Paraben Free</li>\r\n<li>Dermatologist Tested</li>\r\n<li>Oil Free&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Non-Comedogenic (Won\'t Clog Pores)</li>\r\n<li>Exfoliation Factor - Moderate</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>From America\'s #1 scrub brand, this scrub contains 100% natural exfoliants (walnut shell powder and bamboo powder) to unclog dirt and oil from pores for clear, radiant skin.&nbsp;</p>\r\nFun Fact: Spending time with nature has been shown to give you an instant boost of happy!<br /><br /><strong>Uses</strong>: For the management of acne. Helps keep skin clear of new blackheads and acne blemishes</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row item-row\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3><strong>Suggested Use</strong></h3>\r\n<div class=\"prodOverviewDetail\">Squeeze scrub onto fingertips and gently massage onto damp skin. Spread in small circular motions, then rinse and glow! For best results, use 3-4 times a week.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row item-row\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3><strong>Other Ingredients</strong></h3>\r\n<div class=\"prodOverviewIngred\">\r\n<table border=\"1\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<td width=\"50%\"><strong>Active ingredient</strong></td>\r\n<td width=\"50%\"><strong>Purpose</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<td>Salicylic Acid (1.0%)</td>\r\n<td>Acne Treatment</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<td colspan=\"2\"><strong>Inactive ingredients:&nbsp;</strong>Water (aqua), juglans regia (walnut) shell powder, glycerin, glyceryl stearate se, cetearyl alcohol, cocamidopropyl betaine, sodium lauryl sulfoacetate, cetyl alcohol, triethanolamine, cetyl acetate, glyceryl stearate, peg-100 stearate, benzyl alcohol, fragrance (parfum), bambusa arundinacea stem extract, carbomer, ceteareth-20, polysorbate 60, disodium edta, benzoic acid, acetylated lanolin alcohol, sorbic acid, camellia sinensis leaf extract, limonene, linalool, yellow 5 (ci 19140), blue 1 (ci 42090).</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row item-row\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3><strong>Warnings</strong></h3>\r\n<div class=\"prodOverviewDetail\">\r\n<p>For external use only.</p>\r\n<p>When using this product skin irritation and dryness is more likely to occur if you use another topical acne medication at the same time. If irritation occurs, only use one topical acne medication at a time.</p>\r\n<p>Keep out of reach of children. If swallowed get medical help or contact a Poison Control Center right away.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row item-row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Disclaimer</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"disclaimer\" class=\"prodOverviewDetail\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">While iHerb strives to ensure the accuracy of its product images and information, some manufacturing changes to packaging and/or ingredients may be pending update on our site. Although items may occasionally ship with alternate packaging, freshness is always guaranteed. We recommend that you read labels, warnings and directions of all products before use and not rely solely on the information provided by iHerb.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '<div class=\"row item-row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">