(1229, '009-090-004', 'SCRUP&MASQUE Sensitive Skin Aloe Vera', 'SCRUP&MASQUE سكرب ألو فيرا، للبشرة الحساسة', '<div class=\"row item-row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>New Look</li>\r\n<li>Since 1930</li>\r\n<li>Gently Exfoliates for Soothing Refinement</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>This calming facial scrub helps gently draw out impurities and remove dead skin cells, while soothing Aloe Vera and hydrating Jojoba Oil comfort skin. After use, skin is soft and smooth without tightness or discomfort.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row item-row\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3><strong>Suggested Use</strong></h3>\r\n<div class=\"prodOverviewDetail\">\r\n<p>Gently massage onto clean, moistened skin avoiding the eye area. Rinse with warm water and pat dry.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row item-row\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-24\">\r\n<h3><strong>Other Ingredients</strong></h3>\r\n<div class=\"prodOverviewIngred\">\r\n<p>Aqua (water), juglans regia (walnut) shell powder, carbomer, stearyl alcohol, stearic acid, aloe barbadensis leaf juice, hydrogenated jojoba oil, chamomilla recutita (matricaria) flower extract, lavandula angustifolia (lavender) extract, prunus amygdalus dulcis (sweet almond) oil, prunus amygdalus dulcis (sweet almond) seed meal, ascorbic acid, cocamidopropyl betaine, dimethicone, glycerin, glyceryl stearate, isopropyl myristate, kaolin, propylene glycol, potassium hydroxide, sodium chloride, sodium lauryl sulfate, sodium sulfate, tocopheryl acetate, diazolidinyl urea, DMDM hydantoin, methylparaben, phenoxyethanol, propylparaben, benzyl benzoate, benzyl salicylate, butylphenyl methylpropional, citral, hexyl cinnamal, hydroxyisohexyl 3-cylcohexene carboxaldehyde, limonene, fragrance (parfum)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row item-r